Local Char    NAME(255)
Local Char    MASKCODE(255)
Local Clbfile FIELDS(1)

If clalev([F:MSK])=0 : Local File AMSK [MSK] : Endif

NAME = ""
FIELDS = ""
MASKCODE = func GETMASKCODE(CODE)
Read [F:MSK]CODMSK=MASKCODE
If fstat=0
